# Session bootstrap

At the start of a substantive task (or when user says continue / 继续课设):

1. Read `docs/ai/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`, recent `PROGRESS_LOG.md`, `ACTIVE_WORK.md`, `BOOTSTRAP_DIGEST.md`
2. Run `git status --short --branch` if in a git repo
3. Output a **4–8 line** snapshot: platform status, current Feature/Slice, last validation, proposed next step
4. Do **not** infer backlog from `docs/course/` PDF or unchecked old designs

Workflow triggers:

| User intent | Action |
|-------------|--------|
| 计划 / 设计 / 新模块 | Register Feature → Design → Pre-flight |
| slice 完成 / 做完了 | Slice DoD → offer 准备 commit |
| handoff / 交接 | Session note + Progress; Blocked slices marked |
| 准备 commit | Draft only until approval |

See `docs/ai/WORKING_WITH_AI.md`.
